<h2>Brew Method: Pour Over</h2>
<div>
    <div  class=brewimage>
        <%= image_tag "coffee-experiments-pourover-V60.png" %>
    </div>
  <p>
    The classic pour over is a filtered, non-immersion style brew method. Also known as the V-60, bee house and melitta drip, the key identifiers are a clean, refined flavor and smooth finish due to the filtered out oils and particulates.  
  </p>
</div>





